      "id": 1,
      "title": "Anomaly Detection Methodology",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "# Anomaly Detection Center\n\nThis dashboard identifies statistical outliers and unusual behavioral patterns using:\n\n- **Z-Score Method**: Detects values >2 standard deviations from 90-day mean\n- **Volatility Analysis**: Identifies regions with abnormal volatility spikes\n- **Factor Breakdown**: Determines which sub-indices drive anomalies\n- **Historical Context**: Compares current patterns vs historical averages\n\n**Anomaly Thresholds:**\n- **Moderate Anomaly**: Z-score > 2.0 (95th percentile)\n- **Severe Anomaly**: Z-score > 2.5 (99th percentile)\n- **Critical Anomaly**: Z-score > 3.0 (99.7th percentile)\n\n**Related Dashboards:** [Behavior Index Global](http://localhost:3001/d/behavior-index-global) | [Regional Deep Dive](http://localhost:3001/d/regional-deep-dive) | [Risk Regimes](http://localhost:3001/d/risk-regimes)"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Behavior Index with Anomaly Bands (±2σ)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 10,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 6
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "behavior_index{region=\"$region\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Behavior Index",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "avg_over_time(behavior_index{region=\"$region\"}[90d]) + 2 * stddev_over_time(behavior_index{region=\"$region\"}[90d])",
          "legendFormat": "Upper Band (+2σ)",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "expr": "avg_over_time(behavior_index{region=\"$region\"}[90d]) - 2 * stddev_over_time(behavior_index{region=\"$region\"}[90d])",
          "legendFormat": "Lower Band (-2σ)",
          "refId": "C"
